definitions.definition: A mammal of the order Rodentia , characterized by long incisors that grow continuously and are worn down by gnawing .
A person lacking in maturity , social skills , technical competence or intelligence ; lamer .
definitions.label_groups: dated , bulletin board system slang , leetspeak , derogatory
